Package: prml
Type: Package
Title: An implementation of PRML classifier and PRML filter
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Yunran", "Chen", email = "yunran.chen@duke.edu", 
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Yunran Chen <yunran.chen@duke.edu>
Description: The package provides: (1) PRML classifier to test between types of 
    Poisson mixtures. It helps to classify the activation patterns that a single 
    neuron exhibits when preserving information from multiple stimuli. (2) PRML 
    filter to test Poisson versus Poisson mixtures. It helps to screen out 
    over-dispersed Poisson data. 
